node.text: SO grateful to @allureaestheticsllc for helping me achieve the 👄 results I want over the past few months! To help further educate and give behind the scenes, I got to bring you guys along for the process. Getting work done seems to be such a taboo topic, and with the right professionals and plenty of research, it can be done correctly and shouldn't be shameful. I am beyond happy with my results, and I'm looking forward to continuing to work with them throughout 2021.

node.text:
I love when I get to share amazing companies with you guys! @alltrue is my absolute favorite subscription box because they have made it their mission to partner with other mission-driven, “do-good” brands. The products I receive are AMAZING. Every box includes $250+ worth of sustainable, full-sized products for only $49.95. What else do I love? They deliver to your door for FREE!

You get to customize what comes in your Summer Welcome Box and there are a ton of options to choose from! My favorites are the canvas backpack, it’s such a great size and will be great to pack all of our things in for beach trips this summer. I’m also LOVING the Bala Bangles, they are so portable so I can take them and get in a workout anywhere as I continue on my health journey.

If you want to join me and snag a subscription to @alltrue , I was able to get you guys a great deal. Use code Kailyn20 for an extra 20% off your first box at alltrue.com and you’ll get your box for just $39! #alltrue #alltruepartner
